/poem-USSHIXv-7jRQ7Jt3qyrdiA">Phụng hoạ ngự chế “Quang Đức điện thượng cảm thành” - 奉和御製光德殿上感成</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-Ph%C3%BA/author-6psImpn4SbleLfrcnYcyQA">Phạm Đạo Phú</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/Th%E1%BB%A9-v%E1%BA%ADn-Tr%E1%BA%A7n-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-th%C6%B0-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-b%E1%BB%91-ch%C3%A1nh-th%E1%BA%A3o-%C4%91%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/poem-Emk__nQztIejqkAjjYJ2nQ">Thứ vận Trần thượng thư đề Nguyễn bố chánh thảo đường - 次韻陳尚書題阮布政草堂</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Thi%C3%AAn-T%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bc/T%E1%BB%91ng-nam-cung-x%C3%A1-nh%C3%A2n-Tri%E1%BB%87u-T%E1%BB%AD-K%E1%BB%B3-xu%E1%BA%A5t-s%E1%BB%A9-An-Nam/poem-4oPbin-9GDDyzAhsBWqJnw">Tống nam cung xá nhân Triệu Tử Kỳ xuất sứ An Nam - 送南宮舍人趙子期出使安南</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Thi%C3%AAn-T%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bc/author-xrCFopMSKClLzuzHz9jVqg">Tô Thiên Tước</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/Trung-thu-v%C3%B4-nguy%E1%BB%87t-tam-nh%E1%BA%ADt-h%E1%BA%ADu-h%E1%BB%91t-nhi%C3%AAn-t%C3%ACnh-c%E1%BA%A3m-t%C3%A1c/poem-JgdVZfO32jc_MouEhtHb5g">Trung thu vô nguyệt, tam nhật hậu hốt nhiên tình, cảm tác - 中秋無月三日後忽然晴感作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ung/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-linh-c%E1%BB%95-s%E1%BA%AFt/poem-K3s2fyjacYI4dl3bNraddQ">Tương linh cổ sắt - 湘靈鼓瑟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ung/author-H29Qv5SF7vJDgcFb6DeoGg">Vương Ung</a>)<br></div>	</div>
